/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk) NoMergeJoin(k mk t) NoHashJoin(k mk t ci) NoNestLoop(ci k mk t n) NoMergeJoin(ci k mk n t mc) NoMergeJoin(ci k mc mk n t cn) */ select min(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'character-name-in-title'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = t.id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%Bert%'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id;
